    "DT technology elevates BIM models (e.g., for clash detection, cost analysis, project efficiency, etc.)",
    "to a new tier of sophistication, allowing stakeholders to visualize data in real-time.",
    "The advancements and growing research in DT within the AECO industry represent significant progress, they also highlight a range of challenges that prevent its widespread adoption for predictive simulations.",
